        <Meaning id="12a105d9-f092-4562-bd3e-832984356b67" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Cá voi</Vi>
          <En>A large marine mammal of the order Cetacea, typically characterized by a streamlined body, blowhole, and baleen or teeth.</En>
          <Example>Blue whales are the largest animals known to have ever lived.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="ccdcbac0-d78d-4f16-a421-021a881a549f">
